metadata.name: Chestr Genesis Mystery Chest
metadata.description: This mystery chest contains a high-quality artwork NFT or a collectible. It also contains a Chestr Genesis Memento NFT, which grants the holder special privileges in the Chestr community. To open this chest, go to https://chestr.io. Note that this chest NFT gets burned after opening. The chest 3D asset was designed by community creator @GussoAlexandro
